<div class="cms-content">
    <h3>At Confused.com we want to be certain we are treating our customers fairly.</h3>
We have a watertight security and privacy policy in place and promise to look after your personal details with extraordinary care.<br />
<br />
We also operate a <a href="/privacy-and-security/no-spam-policy">no spam policy</a> so we are not bombarding you with emails, and want to make our website as user-friendly as possible by adhering to web accessibility guidelines.<br />
<br />
If you want to know more about how we operate here at Confused.com, you can find out on the pages at the links below.<br />
<br />
<ul class="bullet-tick-list">
    <li><a href="/privacy-and-security/privacy-policy">Read our privacy policy</a></li>
    <li><a href="/privacy-and-security/security">Read our security policy</a></li>
    <li><a href="/about-us/cookie-policy">Read our cookie policy</a></li>
    <li><a href="/privacy-and-security/terms-and-conditions">Read our website terms &amp; conditions</a></li>
    <li><a href="/about-us/accessibility">Read our accessibility statement</a></li>
    <li><a href="/privacy-and-security/no-spam-policy">Read our no spam policy</a></li>
</ul>
<p>If you want to know more about how we operate on our sister site at <a href="https://www.carfused.com/?advertid=1694" target="_blank">Carfused</a>, you can find out on the pages at the links below.</p>
<ul class="bullet-tick-list">
    <li><a href="https://www.carfused.com/privacy-policy?advertid=1677" target="_blank">Read our Carfused privacy policy</a></li>
</ul>
</div>

